<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10090>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Morphological characteristics of Empodisma robustum. A Vegetative shoot with attached leaves and flowers (actual size) B Rhizomes with emerging vegetative shoots (2.5 x actual size) C Vegetative shoot with attached pistillate flower D Pistillate flower with attached bracts E Gynoecium F Mature nut G Vegetative shoot with attached staminate spikelet H Staminate flower with attached bracts I Staminate flower. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10090" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

